@startuml seq_approve_leave
!theme plain
title Sequence Diagram: Leave Request Approval/Rejection Flow

skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "Manager/Admin" as Manager
participant "React SPA (Manager)" as ClientManager
participant "Kong API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Leave Service" as Leave
database "PostgreSQL (HA)" as PG
database "MongoDB" as Mongo
participant "Socket.IO / Redis" as Socket
participant "React SPA (Staff)" as ClientStaff

Manager -> ClientManager : Click "Approve" or "Reject" (with reason)
ClientManager -> Gateway : PUT /api/leaves/:id/status
Gateway -> Leave : Route Request

Leave -> Leave : Verify JWT Token
Leave -> PG : Fetch Leave Request & Check RBAC \n(Manager can only approve their dept)

alt Unauthorized / Invalid State
    Leave -> ClientManager : 403/404 Error
else Authorized
    Leave -> PG : UPDATE leave_requests SET status = 'APPROVED/REJECTED'
    Leave -> Mongo : INSERT LeaveLog (Action: APPROVED/REJECTED)
    
    Note over Leave, PG: Async Notification Task
    Leave -> PG : INSERT INTO announcements \n(target_type = 'INDIVIDUAL')
    
    Leave -> Socket : io.emit("leave_status_update", target_user)
    Leave -> Socket : io.emit("new_announcement", target_user)
    
    Leave -> ClientManager : 200 OK (Updated Successfully)
    ClientManager -> Manager : Refresh UI & Show Toast
    
    Socket -> ClientStaff : Push Events (Status Update & New Notification)
    ClientStaff -> ClientStaff : Show Toast & Update Bell Badge
end
@enduml